        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Endorsing organization</strong></td>
          <td>Post a short statement of endorsement on <a href="https://github.com/continuonai/rcan-spec/issues/13">issue #13</a>; no financial commitment required at this stage</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Technical contributor</strong></td>
          <td>Open a pull request against <code>docs/governance/</code> with proposed amendments</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
